title: Axel Springer bans adblock users from accessing Bild website
text:
Axel Springer bans adblock users from accessing Bild website 
Published By: MacDailyNews.com - Today 
Readers can pay 2.99 euros per month or switch off their adblocker(s) and browse the Bild site for free
